72
00:10:20,077 --> 00:10:23,705
...is that if you could clone
three of him, you'd all be happy.

73
00:10:23,914 --> 00:10:26,833
Okay, tell us, what is your secret?

74
00:10:27,043 --> 00:10:29,210
I'm not sure I can say on TV.

75
00:10:29,462 --> 00:10:32,464
But what I can say is
it's a big secret.

76
00:10:32,715 --> 00:10:34,716
A very big secret.

77
00:10:36,719 --> 00:10:38,887
My goodness gracious!
I can't believe my ears!

78
00:10:39,138 --> 00:10:40,764
Hope my mom's not watching.

79
00:10:41,057 --> 00:10:42,432
