for a special bulletin.

116
00:15:28,344 --> 00:15:31,512
In a special address,
live from the White House...

117
00:15:31,722 --> 00:15:34,182
...the president of the United States.

118
00:15:35,517 --> 00:15:37,268
My fellow Americans...

119
00:15:37,728 --> 00:15:41,022
...our country has suffered
a grievous loss.

120
00:15:41,732 --> 00:15:42,941
Last night...

121
